name: Da nang 1
title: Stay in the heart of Da Nang
desc: Ideally situated in the Hoan Kiem district of Hanoi, DaNang FLORA HOTEL is situated 200 m from Thang Long Water Puppet Theater, 1 km from Hanoi Opera House and less than 1 km from Trang Tien Plaza. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and room service, along with free WiFi. The accommodation features a shared lounge, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests.
